<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Manslayer</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-01 16:32:54</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>One comment on this blade.  Warriors will rave on and on about how much this weapon sucks and how great the exe axe is.<BR>
What we tend to forget is that we are the only ones that can use the exe axe.  All other classes have to suffer through<BR>
high delay 2h slash without the benefit of haste, until hgher levels where they can obtain an fbss or similar haste item.<BR>
For a warrior to use this without the benefit of a haste item would be silly, you can get an exe axe for 800pp, at  <BR>
least on Karana.  But for a Shadow Knight or a Paladin, this is a very good weapon.  Shadow Knights and Paladins aren't<BR>
total tanks, therefore are not as dependent on hitting as hard as they can as fast as they can.  </font></td></tr></table>
